                <note rend="inline" type="source">816.00 Revolutions/10: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Minister in El Salvador</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Curtis</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1931-12-03T19:00:00-05:00"
                            >December 3, 1931—7 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>55. Your December 3, 7 a.m. Who is leading revolution?</p>
                <p>Please keep the Department promptly informed of all important developments by
                    telegraph.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Stimson</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
